    <node id="New Taipei City Crowdfunding Subsidy Program">
      <data key="d0">New Taipei City Crowdfunding Subsidy Program</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">An ongoing initiative launched in 2020 by New Taipei City to assist brands from product verification to market expansion, which has supported 85 teams and raised over NT$245 million cumulatively.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2c0392d6b9fa992204426414fd43866d</data>
